Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(300,300)}我許下夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(300,300)}向著上空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(300,300)}解放軟弱的自己
