Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}已經十年沒看見這片天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好棒哦 好羨慕鳥兒有翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}8點10分 勉強能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:34.82,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:37.97,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:42.48,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒了 天啊 這下怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣的話就進不了家門了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:48.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}轉學第一天就弄丟鑰匙…真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不行不行 我太笨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}找不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早…早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}弄丟鑰匙了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是…聽見你在發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你願意幫我找嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}島上的人都很親切呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}「四島列島可是人情之島 不用擔心」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}奶奶說的沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我昨天才搬來這座久奈島…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你要找的是這個吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}晶也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有…有人在飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 降落請到起降區好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害好厲害 人在天上飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 我叫做倉科明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像是轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科同學找鑰匙時自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}連我的名字都知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我剛剛才自我介紹過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一大早就慢上半拍很麻煩的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我是日向晶也 這位是鳶澤美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們都是久奈濱學院的二年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}話說 我們是不是該趕快去學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這禮拜可是各務老師執勤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.67,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}各務老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}雖然是保健體育老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但她還是生活指導老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}遲到的話肯定會有可怕的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}懲罰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}聽說她會將用個人管道收集來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}學生的黑歷史全部曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼這樣 那可不是人會做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了啦快點 飛過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}起降區在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了 我們飛過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}晶也呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我會跑過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以要怎樣才能飛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你既然穿上我們的制服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也應該聽過反重力鞋的說明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}反重力鞋…就是這雙鞋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}用是…沒用過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒辦法 那就和我一對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}周圍很空曠 禁飛燈也沒有亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 快抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}晶也也來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一…二…起飛喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}起飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼回事 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肯定會掉下去的 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們要掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別睡著啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只要反重力鞋的電源開著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就絕對不會掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯…所以放心享受空中漫步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我在飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只要穿著這雙鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的能飛去任何地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}任何地方…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}他竟然會飛來上學 真難得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼要跑這段坡道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我哪知道 規矩就是規矩啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}5…4…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}3…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}2…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}1！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很好 今天也沒人遲到 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}安全抵達 趕上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安 各務老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她…她就是那位又兇又可怕的老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 別當著本人的面前說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.35,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}噓 噓！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是轉學生倉科吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我就是又兇又可怕的各務葵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能跟我一起來趟辦公室嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}果然分到我們班了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}久奈島是爸爸的故鄉 小時候也來過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這次跟著爸爸工作調動搬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}正想說真是海美天高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就摔了一跤 把鑰匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.98,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總之…能請你先就座嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在教室裡也能看見大海和天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了啦 快點坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鳶澤美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}同學 剛才謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:29.74,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}離遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}日向晶也同學也在這個班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這下正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鳶澤和日向 你們就是倉科的指導員了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}晶也～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天很早下課 已經放學囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天終於開始啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}做什麼呢 吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}無盡可能向我襲來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鳶澤同學的精神和早上不太一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}她有低血壓 早上總是半夢半醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以上午和下午判若兩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}身為她的朋友 還是有點擔心她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只是忠於自我罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一瞬間我還羨慕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 我叫青柳窗果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科同學 等等有空的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要不要來練習反重力鞋？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}你也是指導員 一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道啦 這就來喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請問…指導員是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}反重力鞋的初學者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一定要有指導員跟著指導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}和我都有擔任指導員的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那那…那你就是教練了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請多指教 教練！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天要值日 不能一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}人家好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}回去的路上我要好好補充一下美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐養分！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天沒空啊…我現在是她的指導員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}知道了 我也要陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我是一年A組有坂真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐的手下 或者僕人那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}話說回來 倉科學姐玩遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}PSQ？4DS？還是玩平板或手機遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}順便一提 我不管玩什麼都可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要用什麼分勝負？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.12,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我能開始說明反重力鞋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你知道反重力鞋 即Anti-graviton Shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:45.25,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※螢幕上的英文是動畫寫錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是在發現一種反重力的神奇粒子後 才得以誕生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這個四島列島
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是承認反重力鞋作為一種交通方式的特殊區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}幾年前開始 也認可用它來上下學了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喵 太死板啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說明點到為止就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是 教練！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了 輕輕抬起兩腳的腳後跟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}之後就自己看時機 對鞋子下令起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}它就會啟動 慢慢上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一二…起飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}動起來了 動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我飛起來了…飛起來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科學姐好像很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但像她那樣把手揮來揮去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很快就會搖搖晃晃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 突然平衡就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題的 安全著陸也是反重力鞋的功能之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}剛開始都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我還完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那今天就到這裡 去吃烏龍麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.50,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}烏龍麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 本地名產四島烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我肚子都餓扁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 今天加什麼配菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想想喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們先飛過去了 快點跟上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}起飛喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}出發喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 這家烏龍麵店是有坂同學家開的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哇 是飛魚子 我最喜歡它了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:52.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※飛魚子是四島列島的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這家的烏龍麵加了飛魚汁 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}飛魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※飛魚有ago和tobiuo兩種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在烏龍麵上來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來進行「縱貫久奈 美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐大問答」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我玩 我想多瞭解一下大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼第一題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐的興趣是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是用奶奶傳下來的糠床來醃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.17,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※ぬか床\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}以米糠為主的醃醬菜床
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那第二題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐的三圍是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是我的加上11 7 12
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你為什麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一直承蒙你光顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有點燙 要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r}{\blur4.5}學姐 明天一起上學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們兩個感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那明天見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鳶澤同學飛得真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然而我卻完全不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用那麼在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今後一點點練習就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個 倉科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用那麼消沉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}剛剛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一個人飛起來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但很快就搖晃起來 一下子就掉到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以！明天起請嚴厲指導我 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天不怎麼順利 我好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在天上飛翔好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真期待明天！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鳶澤教練 日向教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今後也請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}隔壁有人搬來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還真沒見過那麼慘的初學者喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科同學 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}聽好了 放鬆身體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是 我在放鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你這不是更用力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}被吹走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不趕快追的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真讓人操心喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是操碎了心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}已經完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}話說 你這是什麼姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總覺得這樣飛起來很穩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是個稀有的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}街頭賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我感覺不像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}等…等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}特地找我挑戰 居然還輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你也真是難堪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以我說了 反抗我佐藤院麗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}跟在太平洋挑戰鯊魚沒兩樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不懂你說什麼…但好不甘心！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊 那個人是窗果的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了 在對決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Flying Circus上能勝過我佐藤院麗子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在久奈濱學院裡是不存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Flying Circus？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是穿反重力鞋進行的一項體育運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 你第一次聽說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼按照約定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}久奈濱學院的院字 我就不客氣收下了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}從今天起你們自報校名 就是缺了院字的久奈濱學了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這…這事拜託高抬貴手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 學校要改名字了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 你先冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這下糟了 我可不要學校被叫久奈濱學！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Come back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個…不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}糟糕 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個 雖然還不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但只要我在Flying Circus上贏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就能把院字還我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這個人是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:32.59,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我是剛轉入久奈濱學院的倉科明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼我要藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}街頭亂鬥啊 好刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是說你想向我挑戰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你對Flying Circus這麼有自信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 我剛剛才聽說這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}今天也是第一次穿反重力鞋獨自飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}開玩笑也要有個限度啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒在開玩笑 我是認真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}算了 既然都說到這個份上 我就跟你比比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:16:59.55,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.10,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個人可是高藤學園的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}高藤學園可是Flying Circus的名校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這下有好戲看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}教練 教我什麼是Flying Circus吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:29.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\bord0\fs45\pos(27,90)}圍繞海上的四個浮標順時針飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:29.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\bord0\fs45\pos(813,18)}時間限制十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:29.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\bord0\fs45\pos(1671,345)}浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:29.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\bord0\fs45\pos(1080,366)}玩家B
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:29.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\bord0\fs45\pos(1158,816)}玩家A
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Flying Circus通常在海面上空由浮標圍成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}邊長300公尺的正方形場地中進行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一對一進行對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}十分鐘內得分較多的一方勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}得分的方式有兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一種是觸碰對方後背
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}另一種是按順序觸碰4個浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你真的是第一次啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那看在是初心者 只設兩個浮標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比賽時間設半場五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只要你能拿到一分 比賽就算是你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼紫苑同學就當裁判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然後你當輔導員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(1087.5,982.5)}Second
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}輔導員是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(764.5,982.5)}Second
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是在地上發出指示的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼教練 拜託你下指示了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為我的翅膀 注入蒼藍的祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你也別發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}比賽從上空那個1號浮標處開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼 起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}準備開始了 各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Set！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我就先拿下一分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}佐藤院得分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎哎…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂 你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}如你所見 正在比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科同學…還有高藤學園的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}競技用反重力鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為什麼要挑戰那種對手？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}人家也沒挑釁 她自找的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼…一頭霧水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}美{\fnHGSSoeiKakupoptai\fs60}咲{\r} {\blur4.5}換我當輔導員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科同學 聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…是 日向教練…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}首先要堵住對方前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}和足球守門員一樣 張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這…這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你以為那種防備就能擋得住我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來…來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在做假動作 去觸碰對手後背！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}總之繞到背後去碰後背！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}背後對吧…看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}佐藤院2分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這哪談得上不知道Flying Circus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}連飛行都還沒個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太小看我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}佐藤院9分 9比0
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看來連1分都拿不到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼第10分 我也不客氣地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你也該投降了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我不會投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}久奈濱學院的院字…由我來保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我一定會拿下1分的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 挺好強嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}倉科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在開始照我說的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說什麼悄悄話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 我要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是現在 把腳合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}保持姿勢 仰起身向上爬升！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎呀 這是要為我的凱旋畫個拱形門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是現在 上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}後背…得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你想得美！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}被躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}到此為止了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}解放軟弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5}翱翔藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5\fs52.5}ダメなダメな自分を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur4.5\fs52.5}今解き放って…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}空中踢轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(930,982.5)}Air kick turn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我…我成功了 拿到1分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}得…得分！那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我叫倉科明日香！
